"title": "5972: unkindness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5972",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Unsympathetic or cruel behaviour. It is contrary to God's character and is condemned in Scripture.</p>\n<h2>Unkindness condemned</h2>\n<h3>In general terms</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:17\">PRO 11:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:5\">PRO 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:20\">PRO 25:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:31-Eph4:32\">EPH 4:31–4:32</a></p>\n<h3>Treatment of enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:43-Matt5:44\">MAT 5:43–5:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:4-Exod23:5\">EXO 23:4–23:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:21\">PRO 25:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:27-Luke6:28\">LUK 6:27–6:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:35\">LUK 6:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:14\">ROM 12:14</a></p>\n<h3>Treatment of the poor</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:31\">PRO 14:31</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:17\">1JN 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:7\">DEU 15:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:14\">DEU 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:13\">PRO 21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:15\">ISA 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:1-Isa10:2\">ISA 10:1–10:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:29\">EZK 22:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:10\">ZEC 7:10</a></p>\n<h3>Treatment of animals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:10\">PRO 12:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:28\">LEV 22:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:6\">DEU 22:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:4\">DEU 25:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:15\">LUK 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:5\">LUK 14:5</a></p>\n<h3>Inhospitality condemned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:9\">1PE 4:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:4\">DEU 23:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41-Matt25:43\">MAT 25:41–25:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:52-Luke9:53\">LUK 9:52–9:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:2\">HEB 13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:10\">3JN 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>Some examples of unkindness</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:2\">1SA 11:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:4\">2SA 12:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:7\">2KI 25:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:5-Neh5:6\">NEH 5:5–5:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:2-Job24:12\">JOB 24:2–24:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:15\">PSA 35:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:20-Ps69:21\">PSA 69:20–69:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:16\">PSA 109:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:4\">EZK 34:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:11\">AMO 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:11\">AMO 5:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:15-Jas2:16\">JAS 2:15–2:16</a></p>\n<h2>God's kindness as a model for believers</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:20\">RUT 2:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:9\">EZR 9:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:7\">ISA 63:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:4\">ROM 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:22\">ROM 11:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:7\">EPH 2:7</a></p>",
